  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 400°F/ Gas 6</p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Peel and chop <strong>potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into bite-sized pieces </p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half </p>\n<p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic </strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong> and <strong>halved tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> to a baking tray </p>\n<p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and tender</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the vegetables are cooking, add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiling water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat and cook for 10-15 min or until fork-tender</p>\n<p>Once cooked, remove from the heat without draining</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1555.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
