            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>shallot</strong> to a <strong>pestle &amp; mortar</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and grind to a paste</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chilli flakes</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and mix to combine</p>\n<p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>chimichurri</strong></p>",
